snippet.title: Mattel Bounce-Off Fun Kids Board Game Trick Shots Challenge Fun With Ckn Toys
snippet.description:
Hi guys, today we are playing with this fun  game Bounce-Off from Mattel Games. Bounce-Off game is simple for everyone to understand and play, but don't be fooled by the easy instructions – the competition is fierce!
Whether you're playing against others by bouncing balls in a frenzied race to match the card or the (slightly) more civilized turn-based play, Bounce-Off game brings the action and the results are wild!
Bounce-Off is a game that everyone can play, regardless of age. This means families, college kids, and young adults.
It's perfect for parties and game nights, and a great way to get the fun going and bring guests together.Set up friendly competitions to see who will be the Bounce-Off champion!

snippet.title: Pie Face Showdown Kids Fun Game Challenge Cream In The Face  With Ckn Toys
snippet.description:
Hi guys, today we are playing PIE FACE SHOWDOWN.this is the second version of Pie Face which is just as fun.
 The hilarious Pie Face Showdown game brings friends and family together for lots of laugh-out-loud fun. First, players load the arm with whipped cream or the included sponge. Then each player places their chin on one of the chin rests and at the count of 3, rapidly mashes the button nearest to them, which activates the hand on the throwing arm. The suspense builds as players try to get the arm to move toward their opponent, and when it gets too close to the pie thrower, it'll spring up, and that player will get creamed! The player who doesn't get "pie-faced" wins.
Thanks for watching guys if you enjoy this video please don't forget to subscribe to CKN Toys.

snippet.title: Superhero Wet Head Game Challenge Water Splashing Fun Kids Board Game Ckn Toys
snippet.description:
Hi guys,today we are so excited to be playing with this Wet Head game from Zing with our Superhero friends Superman,Batgirl,Supergirl and Wonder Woman.Wet Head is a fun water roulette game children can play outdoors for lots of laughs and giggles. Simply fill the tank with water, strap the hat on securely to your head, spin the top and pull one of the pins. Each player has a turn at wearing the hat until the 'trigger' pin is pulled which causes the tank to release the water onto the head of its anxious player. Will you be the next wet head? 
We hope you enjoy this video as much as we love making them.Please don't forget to subscribe.

snippet.title: Fun Kids Game Shark Bite Playtime With Spiderman And CKN
snippet.description:
It's Spider-man Vs Ckn in this epic fun scary kids board game Shark Bite . Get ready to have a REEL-y good time when you play Shark Bite! Snag the fish and be the winner, but if the shark jumps, you’ll be his dinner! Place the fun and colorful sea creatures into the game unit with a snap, and grab your friends to start playing. Players take turns rolling the die and fishing for the sea creatures using the fishing rods. But watch out – you never know when the shark is going to bite!
Thank you Pressman for sending us this game.
